data.description: A wonderful opportunity to own a spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath end unit townhouse that will give you a rare, generous yard space you've been looking for to entertain your guests' for those upcoming memorable summer parties. Freshly painted with new laminate floors throughout the first level. Enjoy the community pool/playground with low HOA fees, a wood burning fireplace and low electricity bills from the newly installed solar panels. (See attached annual solar increase chart) Live on a whisper quiet dead end street with your own private driveway. Get spoiled with the conveniences of a bustling shopping district and bus transportation just walking distance to Forest Ave. Seller is negotiable so book this showing today!
